description: After mobiles start mysteriously flying out of the hands of people in Chennai, Dr Vaseegaran summons his trusted robot Chitti to ward off the bird-shaped supernatural powers of Pakshirajan.

name: Sanju
description: Biopic of the controversial life of actor Sanjay Dutt: his film career, jail sentence, and personal life.

name: Padmaavat
description: Set in medieval Rajasthan, Queen Padmavati is married to a noble king and they live in a prosperous fortress with their subjects until an ambitious Sultan hears of Padmavati's beauty and forms an obsessive love for the Queen of Me...

name: Andhadhun
description: A series of mysterious events change the life of a blind pianist, who must now report a crime that he should technically know nothing of.

name: Simmba
description: Simmba enjoys all the perks of being an amoral and unethical police officer until a life-changing event forces him to choose the righteous path.

name: Thugs of Hindostan
description: A story about one man's love for his nation and another's love for power. An epic adventure filled with edge-of-the-seat thrills and war on the seas.

name: Race 3
description: Relationships and loyalties of a criminal family planning its next big heist are tested when some shocking revelations strike them.

name: Baaghi 2
description: A battle-hardened army officer squares off against drug lords and Russian henchmen to save his ex-lover's kidnapped daughter in the underbelly of Goa, India.

name: Sarkar
description: An NRI businessman learns his vote has been cast by someone else and decides to investigate the matter, eventually finding himself pitted against two corrupt politicians.

name: Badhaai ho
description: A man is embarrassed when he finds out his mother is pregnant.

name: Hichki
description: Suffering from Tourette Syndrome, Naina gets assigned a class of defiant students and must ensure that her students realise their potential.

name: Rangasthalam
description: Chitti Babu begins to suspect his elder brother's life is in danger after they team up to lock horns with their village president and overthrow his unlawful 30 year old regime.

name: Raazi
description: A Kashmiri woman agrees to marry a Pakistani army officer in order to spy on Pakistan during the Indo-Pakistan War of 1971.

name: Zero
description: Through his relationships with two wildly different women, a vertically challenged bachelor with a larger-than-life persona must discover his purpose.

name: Padman
description: Upon realizing the extent to which women are affected by their menses, a man sets out to create a sanitary pad machine and to provide inexpensive sanitary pads to the women of rural India.

name: K.G.F: Chapter 1
description: In the 1970s, a gangster named Rocky goes undercover as a slave to assassinate the owner of a notorious gold mine known as the Kolar Gold Fields.

name: Stree
description: In the small town of Chanderi, the menfolk live in fear of an evil spirit named "Stree" who abducts men in the night. Based on the urban legend of "Nale Ba" that went viral in Karnataka in the 1990s.

name: Bharat Ane Nenu
description: Bharat, a young graduate who becomes the C.M of Andhra Pradesh (pre-div) after his father's demise without any political knowledge, faces challenges in the process of reforming the society.

name: Kaala
description: Kaala is about the life of Nellai / Tirunelveli based Tamils who live in large number in Mumbai.

name: Gold
description: The journey of a man who was instrumental in making India win its first Olympic gold medal as a free nation.

name: Sonu Ke Titu Ki Sweety
description: Titu is going to marry a perfect woman named Sweety. Titu's best-friend Sonu doubts Sweety's character and tries to break the marriage while Sweety tries to do opposite and which leads to war between Bromance and Romance.

name: Raid
description: A fearless income tax officer raids the mansion of the most powerful man in Lucknow after someone mysteriously draws his attention towards the evidence.

name: Aravindha Sametha Veera Raghava
description: A young scion of a powerful family with a long history of violence decides to put an end to the bloodshed which leads him to a path of self discovery.

name: Veere Di Wedding
description: Four girls on their way to find true love discover that their friendship must remain strong until the wedding of a friend named Veer.

name: Geetha Govindam
description: An innocent young lecturer is misunderstood as a pervert and despised by a woman who co-incidentally turns out to be the younger sister of his brother-in-law. Eventually differences subside and love blooms between them.

name: Sui Dhaaga: Made in India
description: It's a heart-warming story of pride and self-reliance capturing the journey of Mauji and his wife Mamta who pursue their passion by overcoming all odds.

name: Dhadak
description: Set in Rajasthan, this love story explores how the protagonists deal with issues like differences between castes and honor killings.

name: 102 Not Out
description: 102 Not Out is a 2018 comedy-drama film, with legendary actor Amitabh Bachchan playing a 102-year-old wanting to break the oldest-man-alive record. Another Bollywood legend Rishi Kapoor plays his sad and grumpy 75-year-old son.

name: Satyameva Jayate
description: An honest cop attempts to hunt down a vigilante who kills corrupt cops by setting them on fire.

name: Kedarnath
description: Mansoor, a reserved and reticent Pithoo, helps pilgrims make an arduous journey upwards to the temple town. His world turns around when he meets the beautiful and rebellious Mukku who draws him into a whirlwind of intense love.

name: Agnyaathavaasi
description: An exiled heir to billionaire, returns after his father was murdered, as a regular employee to find out the killers and make things right in his company.

name: Naa Peru Surya, Naa Illu India
description: Following two violent incidents at a club and a police station, a short tempered soldier is challenged to give up anger if he wants to fulfill his dream of serving at the borders.

name: Chekka Chivantha Vaanam
description: A bloody power struggle erupts between three brothers who are vying to take over the family business following the death of their father.

name: Parmanu: The Story of Pokhran
description: Ashwat Raina and his teammates arrive in Pokhran to re-conduct a confidential nuclear test, where they face challenges from the American Lacrosse satellite and local spies.

name: Thaanaa Serndha Koottam
description: Angered by the corruption that stopped him from becoming a CBI officer, a young man forms a gang who pose as CBI officers and raids the corrupt.

name: Mahanati
description: Biography of Savitri, an actress from South India movie industry, who ruled the industry for two decades during 50s and 60s.

name: Kadaikutty Singam
description: Gunasingam, a family-loving farmer who hails from a small town, tries his best to keep his big family united despite him being misunderstood by many.

name: Bhaagamathie
description: IAS officer Chanchala Reddy is imprisoned in a haunted house, while she is interrogated by law enforcers investigating a politician they suspect of corruption.

name: Kayamkulam Kochunni
description: Dreaded by the rich and corrupt and revered by the poor and downtrodden, Kayamkulam Kochunni was a Robin Hood of sorts. Chronicles the life and times of the legendary 19th century highwayman, and how he rose from his humble beginn...

name: Irumbu Thirai
description: A soldier takes on a gang of cyber criminals when money goes missing from his account.

name: Seema Raja
description: A youngster who belongs to a royal family needs to play saviour to his villagers.

name: Vada Chennai
description: A young carrom player in north Chennai becomes a reluctant participant in a war between two warring gangsters.

name: Carry on Jatta 2
description: Orphan Jass dreams of settling down in Canada, but isn't eligible to immigrate. He must find a non-resident Indian girl to marry so he can fulfill his dream.
Two high school sweethearts meet at a reunion after 22 years and reminisce about their past.

name: October
description: A group of interns are going through the usual grind when suddenly an accident changes their lives. The protagonist can't get let go of it and becomes obsessed with it. What does it all lead to? Is it love or something else?

name: Batti Gul Meter Chalu
description: The life of three friends takes a tragic turn due to an inflated electricity bill, which leads to a courtroom drama and social awakening.

name: Odiyan
description: The story of the Odiyan clan, one of the most dreaded, shape-shifting black magicians in the world which ruled the darkness of night through during the pre-electrification era in Kerala.

name: SaamyÂ²
description: The son of Aarusaamy becomes a cop and takes on the criminal who murdered his parents.

name: Vishwaroopam 2
description: RAW agent Wisam Ahmad Kashmiri prevents an al-Qaida terrorist from executing a massive attack on New York. He must now wade through further traps and conspiracies to thwart a new plot against three democratic nations.

name: Sandakozhi 2
description: Balu and his father have to protect a young man from a woman who has sworn vengeance on his entire clan.

name: Thamizh Padam 2
description: A stringent cop tries all the possible ways to nab a dreaded don who poses a big threat to the society.

name: Njan Prakashan
description: Pining for a lavish life abroad, a lazy but lovable guy-next-door crafts a scam to avoid a career in nursing and find a wealthy spouse to secure a visa.

name: Jai Simha
description: A rowdy mechanic with a golden-heart turns into a body guard to save a family from goons.
